  1→//! End-to-end integration test for the Arcan ↔ Lago bridge.
  2→//!
  3→//! Exercises the full cycle: Arcan events → Lago journal → read back →
  4→//! AppStateProjection → verify reconstructed state.
  5→
  6→use std::sync::Arc;
  7→
  8→use arcan_core::protocol::{
